<li id="cite_note-term-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-term_18-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://mpc.byu.edu/Exhibitions/Of%20Earth%20Stone%20and%20Corn/Activities/Native%20American%20Pottery.dhtml" class="external text" title="http://mpc.byu.edu/Exhibitions/Of%20Earth%20Stone%20and%20Corn/Activities/Native%20American%20Pottery.dhtml" rel="nofollow">"Other meanings"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://mpc.byu.edu/Exhibitions/Of%20Earth%20Stone%20and%20Corn/Activities/Native%20American%20Pottery.dhtml" class="external free" title="http://mpc.byu.edu/Exhibitions/Of%20Earth%20Stone%20and%20Corn/Activities/Native%20American%20Pottery.dhtml" rel="nofollow">http://mpc.byu.edu/Exhibitions/Of%20Earth%20Stone%20and%20Corn/Activities/Native%20American%20Pottery.dhtml</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-01-20</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Other+meanings&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmpc.byu.edu%2FExhibitions%2FOf%2520Earth%2520Stone%2520and%2520Corn%2FActivities%2FNative%2520American%2520Pottery.dhtml&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Malware"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> The term "grayware" is also used to describe a kind of Native American pottery and has also been used by some working in computer technology as slang for the human brain. <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.techweb.com/encyclopedia/defineterm.jhtml?term=grayware" class="external text" title="http://www.techweb.com/encyclopedia/defineterm.jhtml?term=grayware" rel="nofollow">"grayware definition"</a>. TechWeb.com<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.techweb.com/encyclopedia/defineterm.jhtml?term=grayware" class="external free" title="http://www.techweb.com/encyclopedia/defineterm.jhtml?term=grayware" rel="nofollow">http://www.techweb.com/encyclopedia/defineterm.jhtml?term=grayware</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-01-02</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=grayware+definition&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=TechWeb.com&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.techweb.com%2Fencyclopedia%2Fdefineterm.jhtml%3Fterm%3Dgrayware&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Malware"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-webopedia-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-webopedia_19-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://webopedia.com/TERM/g/greyware.html" class="external text" title="http://webopedia.com/TERM/g/greyware.html" rel="nofollow">"Greyware"</a>. <i>What is greyware? - A word definition from the Webopedia Computer Dictionary</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://webopedia.com/TERM/g/greyware.html" class="external free" title="http://webopedia.com/TERM/g/greyware.html" rel="nofollow">http://webopedia.com/TERM/g/greyware.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-06-05</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Greyware&amp;rft.atitle=What+is+greyware%3F+-+A+word+definition+from+the+Webopedia+Computer+Dictionary&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwebopedia.com%2FTERM%2Fg%2Fgreyware.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Malware"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
